$ Office Ribbon: File -> Options -> Add-ins
@ Add-ins

View and manage → Microsoft/Office/add-in[Office Add-ins]

The *Go* button at the bottom allows to enable or disable *Add-ins*.

{ Drop Down: Manage

  { Excel

    In Excel, the Drop Down *Manage* has the item *Disabled Items* which allows to enable → Windows/dirs/Users/username/AppData/Roaming/Microsoft/Excel/XLSTART/Personal_xlsb[`Personal.xlsb`] if it is disabled.

  }

}

sa:
  The menu → Microsoft/Office/Excel/GUI/Ribbon/tabs/Insert/Add-ins[Insert -> Add-ins]
